description:
Located in one of Crookwell's rapidly growing new estates, this 1011m2 slightly undulating block is quietly located at the end of a cul-de-sac with district views and ample space, oozing potential.

For savvy investors, first home buyers, or downsizers looking to build their forever home, this is perfect. Crookwell offers all the comforts of country living with schools, shops, transport and cafes as well as easy access to Bathurst, Canberra, Goulburn and approximately 30 minutes to the Hume Highway.

For further information please contact Mark Heaton on 0401 683 977.
